<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Advent 1</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> (Nov. 30)<br>
Jeremiah 33:14-16 (Righteous Branch from David’s line)<br>
1 Thessalonians 3:9-13 (Be strong until Jesus comes again)<br>
Luke 21:25-36 (Your redemption is drawing near)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Advent 2</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> (Dec. 7)<br>
Malachi 3:1-4 (A messenger will prepare the way)<br>
Philippians 1:3-11 (Paul - a faithful messenger)<br>
Luke 3:1-6 (The Advent voice of John the Baptizer)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Advent 3</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> (Dec. 14) - Sunday of Rejoicing (hence the pink candle)<br>
Zephaniah 3:14-18 (Sing, O Daughter of Zion)<br>
Philippians 4:4-7 (Rejoice always in the Lord)<br>
Luke 3:7-18 (God’s messenger prepares the way)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Advent 4</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> (Dec. 21)<br>
Micah 5:2-4 )A Ruler will come out of Bethlehem)<br>
Hebrews 10:5-10 (Christ came to God’s Will)<br>
Luke 1:39-45 (Mary’s Song of Praise) <p>In Christ,<br>
